tt |access-date=11 March 2020 |last3=Sfrintzeris |first3=Yasmin |last4=R\u00f8set |first4=Hanna Haug |last5=breaking-avdeling |first5=Carina Hunshamar og VGs |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320002130/https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona-viruset/ |archive-date=20 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"VG\">{{cite web |url=https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona/ |title=Corona-viruset: Slik spres viruset i Norge og verden. Kart og statistikk |publisher=Vg.no |access-date=2020-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329020316/https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona/ |archive-date=29 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|DNK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Denmark|Denmark]]\n|6,318\n|285\n|2,235\n|<ref name=\"STPS numbers\" />\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|CZE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Czech Republic|Czech Republic]]\n|6,022\n|143\n|519\n|<ref name=\"CZE\">{{cite web |url=https://onemocneni-aktualne.mzcr.cz/covid-19 |title=P\u0159ehled situace v \u010cR: COVID-19 |date=27 March 2020 |website=mzcr.cz |language=cs |url-status=live |access-date=27 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322121846/https://onemocneni-aktualne.mzcr.cz/covid-19 |archive-date=22 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|SRB}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Serbia|Serbia]]<!-- Please only include the figures for Serbia excluding Kosovo here, as reported by WHO, since figures for Kosovo are in a separate row below --> \n|4,054\n|85\n|400\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200323-sitrep-63-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=d97cb6dd_2 |title=Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19)Situation Report \u201363 |last=World Health Organization |website=www.who.int |language=en |access-date=24 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323205954/https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/situation-reports/20200323-sitrep-63-covid-19.pdf?sfvrsn=d97cb6dd_2 |archive-date=23 March 2020 |ur